      • getSize

        public int getSize()

        Gets the size of the competitor in bytes. The fields size is:

        • firstName: 4 + length
        • lastName: 4 + length
        • shorName: 4 + length
        • description: 4 + length
        • nationality: 4 + length
        • color: 1 + color
        • ToT: 8
        • ToD: 8
        • picture: 1 + picture
        • class: class length
        • team: team length
        Specified by:
        getSize in interface com.tractrac.util.lib.api.serialize.ISerializable
        Overrides:
        getSize in class AbstractMetadataContainer
        Returns:
        the total size of bytes
